sku.Description: Model representing SKU for Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

location.Description: Region where the Azure resource is located.

provisioningState.Description: Provisioning state of the Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

hostSuffix.Description: DNS suffix for public endpoints running in the Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

dataPlaneFqdn.Description: DNS name for accessing DataPlane services

targetContainerHostApiServerFqdn.Description: DNS of the target container host's API server

targetContainerHostResourceId.Description: Resource ID of the target container host

targetContainerHostCredentialsBase64.Description: Credentials of the target container host (base64).

name.Description: The name of the SKU for Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

tier.Description: The tier of the SKU for Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

targetContainerHostResourceId.Description: Resource ID of the target container host mapped to the Azure Dev Spaces Controller.

connectionDetailsList.Description: List of Azure Dev Spaces Controller connection details.

orchestratorSpecificConnectionDetails.Description: Base class for types that supply values used to connect to container orchestrators

kubeConfig.Description: Gets the kubeconfig for the cluster.
